Enums/Command.html#/s:8TeslaKit7CommandO.name: setValetMode(_:)
Enums/Command.html#/s:8TeslaKit7CommandO.abstract: Sets valet mode on or off with a PIN to disable it from within the car. Reuses last PIN from previous valet session.
